        "TileImage": "$($repository 9a17757d-812c-4018-a95c-04b2bddbdbe0).Image",
        "Description": "I&apos;ve spent almost an entire year planning my retirement dinner, hundreds of guests have arrived and these slackers are holding everything up! What a waste of money hiring these useless people. I don&apos;t want to have to deal with a drawn out dispute by firing them all, I&apos;m too busy for that, it&apos;s faster and cheaper to hire you. Get rid of these sloths.",
